    <description><![CDATA[Green Hill community, from Mount Pleasant north on FM 2152 then east on CR 1660<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 350 CR 1660, Mount Pleasant<br/><br/><b>Marker Text:</b> Presbyterian Church Established in 1860]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-94.990525,33.249693,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
